==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Emulator
<hw>Em"u*la`tor</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>aemulator</ets>.]</ety> <def>One who emulates, or strives to equal
or surpass.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>As Virgil rivaled Homer, Milton was the <qex>emulator</qex> of
both.</q> <rj><qau>Bp. Warburton.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Emulatory</ent>⟦br⟧
